1
00:00:08,399 --> 00:00:08,960
Brother San

2
00:00:10,119 --> 00:00:11,439
The stuff from the hills is good today

3
00:00:11,439 --> 00:00:12,399
I came to buy again

4
00:00:14,840 --> 00:00:15,279
Don't

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:16,600
No

6
00:00:17,239 --> 00:00:17,959
It's not convenient

7
00:00:18,399 --> 00:00:19,079
Don't come in

8
00:00:19,639 --> 00:00:20,360
Sister-in-law

9
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,000
Is Brother San here?

10
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:23,959
I know the rules

11
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,399
I won't go in

12
00:00:25,959 --> 00:00:27,239
I'll leave right after I get the stuff

13
00:00:31,159 --> 00:00:32,040
Sold

14
00:00:32,799 --> 00:00:33,400
Him

15
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:34,759
Sold him too

16
00:00:38,319 --> 00:00:39,119
I said

17
00:00:39,639 --> 00:00:40,560
Sold

18
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,599
Meat is meat anyway

19
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:54,360
My brother Liu Ping has always been a good man

20
00:00:55,599 --> 00:00:56,919
Our family

21
00:00:56,919 --> 00:01:00,880
has never done anything wicked

22
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,879
Why is this happening?

23
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:06,839
Why?

24
00:01:06,839 --> 00:01:08,559
Where exactly is your brother Liu Ping now?

25
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,360
Right now, only you

26
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,160
can help Liu Ping

27
00:01:15,559 --> 00:01:17,199
help your parents and yourself too

28
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:22,160
I really don't know where he is

29
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,480
He only said

30
00:01:25,199 --> 00:01:26,199
it was a pity

31
00:01:26,599 --> 00:01:30,839
he can't care for our parents anymore

32
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,720
Mom

33
00:02:06,559 --> 00:02:07,319
I'm going to get some water

34
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,240
Son

35
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,520
Come back soon

36
00:02:16,399 --> 00:02:17,600
Cover all entrances and exits

37
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:50,119
Wood and motor oil smell

38
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:52,279
That doctor is suspicious

39
00:02:52,679 --> 00:02:53,320
I'm with her

40
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,039
I'll go after her

41
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,039
Okay, be careful

42
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,800
Attention, everyone

43
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:01,039
Liu Ping may be disguised as a doctor

44
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:03,080
armed and escaping through the crowd

45
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,559
Everyone, watch every exit closely

46
00:03:04,559 --> 00:03:05,440
Get ready to make the arrest

47
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:10,880
Liu Ping

48
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:11,880
Stop

49
00:03:22,679 --> 00:03:23,360
Stop

50
00:03:25,559 --> 00:03:26,160
Don't move

51
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:27,679
Liu Ping

52
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,320
Calm down

53
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,080
Put the knife down

54
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:32,720
Calm down

55
00:03:32,839 --> 00:03:33,479
You all

56
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,520
Shut up

57
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:35,240
Liu Ping

58
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:37,839
Calm down

59
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:39,800
Let's talk

60
00:03:40,279 --> 00:03:41,119
There's nothing to talk about

61
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:43,039
I'm dead anyway

62
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,440
Before I die, I'll take someone down with me

63
00:03:44,839 --> 00:03:45,399
Liu Ping

64
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,199
Calm down

65
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,559
What happened with you and your sister

66
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:50,839
we all know

67
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,839
We all feel for you

68
00:03:52,839 --> 00:03:54,440
especially this young woman

69
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,679
You still have a chance to turn over a new leaf

70
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,199
You're not an evil man

71
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,559
I am an evil man

72
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,720
I'm guilty

73
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,639
I hate that I didn't kill him sooner

74
00:04:03,119 --> 00:04:04,720
My sister would've suffered less

75
00:04:05,279 --> 00:04:06,199
Now look

76
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,240
Let's all die together

77
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:14,639
How is it?

78
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,040
Are you okay?

79
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,040
I'm fine

80
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:17,799
It's just that

81
00:04:18,239 --> 00:04:19,239
my neck hurts a little

82
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,959
You were completely reckless, you know that?

83
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,399
If anything had happened to you

84
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,959
how would I explain it to your station?

85
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:25,959
Sorry, Captain Duan

86
00:04:26,239 --> 00:04:27,320
This time it was urgent

87
00:04:27,320 --> 00:04:28,160
I promise it won't happen again

88
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,040
Take him away

89
00:04:33,679 --> 00:04:34,239
Move

90
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:39,959
Not bad

91
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:41,679
Your shooting was very accurate

92
00:04:41,679 --> 00:04:42,799
And you're quick-witted too

93
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,239
But you were way too impulsive

94
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,160
What if I didn't know Morse Code?

95
00:04:47,119 --> 00:04:48,480
I checked up on you

96
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,760
I know you understand cryptography

97
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,079
That's why I signaled you

98
00:04:52,239 --> 00:04:53,040
You investigated me?

99
00:04:55,359 --> 00:04:56,839
Why are you so suspicious?

100
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,279
Can't I show some concern

101
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,160
for my own colleague?

102
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,320
Why do you know Morse Code?

103
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,920
My dad taught me when I was little

104
00:05:03,239 --> 00:05:04,119
My dad said

105
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,600
this was between him and me

106
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:06,959
our father-daughter code

107
00:05:09,559 --> 00:05:10,519
Sorry for the trouble

108
00:05:10,799 --> 00:05:11,640
Comrade Lin Shen

109
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:12,839
Let's get back to the team

110
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,640
We still have a lot to do

111
00:05:15,239 --> 00:05:16,040
All right

112
00:06:08,679 --> 00:06:09,679
You're pretty impressive

113
00:06:10,359 --> 00:06:12,000
You can even kill wolves

114
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,079
Then again

115
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,720
you sold plenty of poached goods with your brother-in-law

116
00:06:19,359 --> 00:06:20,359
That money from last time

117
00:06:21,239 --> 00:06:21,880
pay me back

118
00:06:22,119 --> 00:06:22,799
Money?

119
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,359
What money?

120
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,239
That

121
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,160
Go ask Qiao Sanbao for it

122
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,640
What do you mean?

123
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,200
That loser

124
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,519
lost five thousand to me yesterday

125
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,480
Why don't you pay it back for your brother-in-law

126
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,959
Or else

127
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,760
Qiao Sanbao said

128
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,119
your sister could pay the debt

129
00:06:53,799 --> 00:06:54,600
You know

130
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,600
your sister looks rough

131
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,519
but she's pretty tender underneath

132
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:11,239
After I killed the wolf, I dragged it here

133
00:08:11,239 --> 00:08:12,959
I really feel it wasn't worth it for them

134
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,679
For those two scumbags

135
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,000
they threw their whole lives away

136
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,200
They could've had much better lives

137
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,119
No matter how deep a personal grudge is

138
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,959
you still can't be your own judge

139
00:08:25,679 --> 00:08:26,880
If everyone acted like this

140
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,079
and copied each other

141
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,839
then what would become of

142
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,679
this society?

143
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,200
As police officers,

144
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,679
our job is to cut off this

145
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,440
chain of you kill me, I kill you

146
00:08:37,479 --> 00:08:38,280
The net of the law

147
00:08:38,719 --> 00:08:39,400
must spread wide

148
00:08:39,599 --> 00:08:40,400
and pull tight

149
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,320
It may tighten late,

150
00:08:42,719 --> 00:08:43,719
but no one can escape

151
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,200
As for legal education,

152
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,719
we have to talk about it often

153
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,640
every single day

154
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:49,760
Captain Duan

155
00:08:50,359 --> 00:08:51,400
I'll go over and check

156
00:08:57,359 --> 00:08:58,119
how she's doing

157
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,200
What do you mean, how?

158
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,280
She's pretty sharp

159
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:05,719
Maybe you two will be good partners

160
00:09:52,719 --> 00:09:54,359
Anyone who bullied my sister

161
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,039
deserved to die

162
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,960
Little Crazy

163
00:10:27,599 --> 00:10:28,479
Little Crazy

164
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,080
Come here

165
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,479
Come over here

166
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,359
Little Crazy

167
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,239
What is it? You're so hungry

168
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,080
Who did you go out and fight today?

169
00:10:48,359 --> 00:10:50,280
Your little paws are all black

170
00:10:51,559 --> 00:10:52,719
Did you win or lose?

171
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,359
Tell me

172
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:00,719
If you can't win, then run

173
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,599
Got it?

174
00:11:03,159 --> 00:11:04,960
Don't let them scratch you up

175
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,520
Eat slowly

176
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:22,119
Don't move

177
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:27,080
What are you doing? We're on the same side

178
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,440
Could it have been back then?

179
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,960
She's pretty sharp

180
00:12:33,479 --> 00:12:35,359
Maybe you two will be good partners

181
00:12:35,479 --> 00:12:37,000
You've worked hard, Comrade Lin Shen

182
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,359
So what does this make us?

183
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,400
No acquaintance without a fight

184
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:42,799
Officer Lin is heroic and dashing

185
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,119
Sister Lin

186
00:12:44,119 --> 00:12:45,479
with agile moves

187
00:12:45,719 --> 00:12:46,960
Comrade Lin

188
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,359
with such commanding presence

189
00:12:48,719 --> 00:12:49,559
Beautiful Lin

190
00:12:50,119 --> 00:12:52,119
Senior Lin, please look after me

191
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,080
and give me lots of guidance

192
00:12:58,599 --> 00:12:59,440
Sorry for the trouble
